	body
		nav#ftco-navbar.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-dark.ftco_navbar.bg-dark.ftco-navbar-light
			.container
				a.navbar-brand(href="index.html") HITOMEMO
				button.navbar-toggler(type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#ftco-nav" aria-controls="ftco-nav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation")
					span.oi.oi-menu
					|  Menu
				#ftco-nav.collapse.navbar-collapse
					ul.navbar-nav.ml-auto
						li.nav-item.active
							a.nav-link(href="#") Home
						// if not logged in : jump into login page, already logged in : servie page
						li.nav-item
							a.nav-link(href="#") Memoru
						// if not logged in : jump into login page, already logged in : servie page
						li.nav-item
							a.nav-link(href="#") Sign in
		// END nav
		section.home-slider.ftco-degree-bg
			.slider-item
				.overlay
				.container
					.row.slider-text.align-items-center.justify-content-center
						.col-md-10.ftco-animate.text-center
							h1.mb-4
								| Note about  
								strong.typewrite(data-period="4000" data-type='[ "Her.", "Him.", "They.", "We." ]')
									span.wrap
							p HITOMEMOは顔で人を識別し、メモを残します。仕事でもプライベートでも忘れそうな時やその日の感想など、なんでもメモリましょう！
							p.my-5
								a.btn.btn-primary.btn-outline-white.px-4.py-3.popup-vimeo(href="https://vimeo.com/45830194")
									span.ion-ios-person.mr-2
									|  Start Now!
		// END slider
		section.ftco-section.ftco-degree-bg
			.container
				.row.justify-content-center.mb-5.pb-5
					.col-md-7.text-center.heading-section.ftco-animate
						span.subheading HITOMEMOについて
						h2 人の顔、覚えていますか？
				.row
					.col-md-6.col-lg-3.d-flex.align-self-stretch.ftco-animate
						.media.block-6.services.d-block.text-center
							.d-flex.justify-content-center
								.icon.color-1.d-flex.justify-content-center.mb-3
									span.align-self-center.icon-layers
							.media-body.p-2
								h3.heading メモを残す
								p 名前・職業・所属などの情報はなくても大丈夫です。その人のことをあなたの言葉で残しましょう。
					.col-md-6.col-lg-3.d-flex.align-self-stretch.ftco-animate
						.media.block-6.services.d-block.text-center
							.d-flex.justify-content-center
								.icon.color-2.d-flex.justify-content-center.mb-3
									span.align-self-center.icon-gears
							.media-body.p-2
								h3.heading わかりやすい
								p HITOMEMOはユーザの経験を最優先とするシンプルでわかりやすいサービスを目指します。
					.col-md-6.col-lg-3.d-flex.align-self-stretch.ftco-animate
						.media.block-6.services.d-block.text-center
							.d-flex.justify-content-center
								.icon.color-3.d-flex.justify-content-center.mb-3
									span.align-self-center.icon-paper-plane
							.media-body.p-2
								h3.heading メモを共有する
								p 自分の言葉を共有しよう。（共有がなければ削除）
					.col-md-6.col-lg-3.d-flex.align-self-stretch.ftco-animate
						.media.block-6.services.d-block.text-center
							.d-flex.justify-content-center
								.icon.color-4.d-flex.justify-content-center.mb-3
									span.align-self-center.icon-live_help
							.media-body.p-2
								h3.heading 質問がある
								p あなたの質問はHITOMEMOチームにとっては大事なフィードバックです。いつでも我々に連絡してください。
		footer.ftco-footer.ftco-bg-dark.ftco-section
			.container
				.row
					.col-md.mb-5.hitomemo-pad-left-15
						.ftco-footer-widget.mb-2
							h2.ftco-heading-2 Members
